Package: nrsaqaapp
Title: NRSA QA Application
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Oklahoma Water Resources Board", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nrsa-qa@owrb.ok.gov")
Description: A Shiny application for quality assurance review of National
    Rivers and Streams Assessment (NRSA) monitoring data. Supports data
    loading via Excel file upload or direct AWQMS ODBC connection, with
    site-visit summaries, an interactive site map, detailed per-site QA
    review, and batch QA reporting across all sites.
